obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line `This Act may be called the Parel Investments and Trading Private Limited and`
  line `Domestic Gas Private Limited (Taking Over of Management) Repeal Act, 2005.`
obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_2:
  sectionId (67272)
  sectionNo (2)
  orderNo 2
  title `Repeal and saving.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_2_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_32_0_00012_200514_1657789728848&sectionId=67272&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_32_0_00012_200514_1657789728848
obj_root_law_sections_2_content:
  string
  line `(1) The Parel Investments and Trading Private Limited and Domestic Gas`
  line `Private Limited (Taking Over of Management) Act, 1979 (29 of 1979) is hereby repealed.;`
  line
  line `(2) On the repeal of the Parel Investments and Trading Private Limited and Domestic Gas Private`
  line `Limited (Taking Over of Management) Act, 1979 (29 of 1979) the management of the Parel Investments`
  line `and Trading Private Limited and Domestic Gas Private Limited shall be vested and deemed to have been vested in the respective board of directors of the said Companies to be appointed after such repeal and`
  line `possession of the assets of the said Companies relating to their business other than the business relating to`
  line `liquefied petroleum gas and not taken over by the Central Government by the Act so repealed shall be`
  line `deemed to have been taken over by, and continued with, the said Companies through their respective`
  line `board of directors, as may be appointed in accordance with the law for the time being in force.`
  line
  line `(3) Notwithstanding such repeal and without prejudice to the provisions contained in the General`
  line `Clauses Act, 1897 (10 of 1897) with respect to repeals, anything done or action taken including any`
  line `agreement entered into under any provision of the Parel Investments and Trading Private Limited and`
  line `Domestic Gas Private Limited (Taking Over of Management) Act, 1979 (29 of 1979), by the Central`
  line `Government or the Custodian appointed by it shall continue to be in force and have effect as if this Act`
  line `had not been passed.`
obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes:
  string
  line
